text: Chagan () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Chagansky Selsoviet, Kamyzyaksky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 1,464 as of 2010. There are 33 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Astrakhan, 30 km from Kamyzyak. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kamyzyaksky District
title: Chagan, Astrakhan Oblast
